Interface JobTemplateSelectable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntitySelectable<JobTemplate>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JobTemplateField, JobTemplateLink

    public interface JobTemplateSelectable
extends EntitySelectable<JobTemplate>
    Interface to enable OData entity selectors for JobTemplate. This interface is used by JobTemplateField and JobTemplateLink.

    Available instances:

    • JOB_TEMPLATE_NAME
    • JOB_TEMPLATE_VERSION
    • JOB_TEMPLATE_STEP_COUNT
    • JOB_PERIODIC_GRANULARITY
    • JOB_REPORT_NAME
    • JOB_USER_NAME
    • JOB_PERIODIC_VALUE
    • JOB_TEMPLATE_TEXT
    • CREATION_DATE_TIME
    • CREATION_USER_NAME
    • LAST_CHANGE_DATE_TIME
    • LAST_CHANGE_USER_NAME
    • SUPPORTS_TEST_MODE_IND
